Class SelectedValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • lecho.lib.hellocharts.model.SelectedValue

  • public class SelectedValue
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds selected values indexes, i.e. for LineChartModel it will be firstIndex=lineIndex; secondIndex=valueIndex.
